reviewText: Great, unique, inspiring, instrumental music! I will use it as prelude music at my wedding and enjoy it at home as well!

I have only seen part of this beautiful, faith inspired DVD. The music, guitar and cello, is moving, the scenes that accompany the music are works of art! I would highly recommend this DVD to anyone who is moved by artists, who can convey passion, sensuality, and a sense of peace, through their instruments. A feast for the soul.
